	   <tr><td>Journal Rating:</td><td>Unrated</td></tr><tr><td>Email:<td><a href=Mailto:Talavir@allakhazam.com>Talavir@allakhazam.com</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 id=headerrow>Bio:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><p>I am called Talavir. By the grace of the Mother, I am a wandering minstrel of the Woodland Elves of Faydark.  With my brown hair and green eyes, I tend to favor my mother however people who knew my father tell me they can see in me my father's features, his intensity of purpose, and strength of character.</p>

<p>Although as a member of a family of troubadours I have considered myself a bard all my life, I am now taking formal training to become a Bard and study at the Songweaver's Stump in Kelethin.</p>

<p><i>OOC: I can be found on Lanys T'Vyl usually between 8pm and midnight weekdays and after 2pm on weekends, but not every day.  I am in the U. S. Central timezone (UTC-06:00)</i></p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></center>
